  }), mdx("p", null, "I'd like to use this space to document various Lean tools, methodologies, and post thoughts or experiences from my own learning.  But first, it might help to define what Lean means to me."), mdx("h2", null, "What is Lean?"), mdx("p", null, "According to LEI's ", mdx("a", _extends({
